          you cannot play a single card on any group!  See
            Humans can discard one card no matter how many actions
            they play.
            Elves can discard TWO cards if they play NO actions.
            Dwarves can discard up to all FOUR cards if they play
            no Actions in their turn.
          Once you discard that is THE END of your turn!
      E = End your Turn and come back to the BBS
      F = Use Fire Card.  See Fire Rules
      P = Play any other card than a fire card.
